PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1998-1333 of July 16, 1998, by deleting the words "Mrs. Claudette Bradshaw" and "Minister for International Cooperation" therefrom; and appointment of DENIS PARADIS, a member of the House of Commons, as Parliamentary Secretary to the Minister for International Cooperation for a period terminating July 15, 1999.
